<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Emerge Digital IT Solutions LLC collects, uses, and protects personal data, in line with UAE Federal Decree-Law No. 45 of 2021 (PDPL)."
>
  <p>
    Emerge Digital IT Solutions LLC (<strong>"Emerge Digital"</strong>, <strong>"we"</strong>,
    <strong>"us"</strong>) respects your privacy. This policy explains what personal data we
    collect when you visit <strong>emergedigital.com</strong> or engage our services, how we
    use it, and the rights you have over it. We handle personal data in line with UAE Federal
    Decree-Law No. 45 of 2021 on the Protection of Personal Data (the <strong>PDPL</strong>) and
    applicable GCC data-protection requirements.
  </p>

  <h2>Data we collect</h2>
  <p><strong>Information you give us.</strong> When you submit the contact or briefing-request form, subscribe to insights, or otherwise correspond with us, we collect your name, business email, company, and the contents of your message.</p>
  <p><strong>Information collected automatically.</strong> When you browse the site we collect standard analytics data — pages viewed, referring source, approximate location, browser and device type — through cookies and similar technologies. See our <a href="/legal/cookies/">Cookies Policy</a>.</p>

  <h2>How we use your data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To respond to your enquiry and arrange briefing or strategy calls.</li>
    <li>To provide, operate, and improve our services and this website.</li>
    <li>To send you material you have requested, such as insights updates.</li>
    <li>To meet our legal, regulatory, and contractual obligations.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Our legal bases under the PDPL are, as applicable: your <strong>consent</strong>; the
    performance of a contract or steps taken at your request before entering one; our
    <strong>legitimate business interests</strong> in operating and growing the business; and
    compliance with a legal obligation.
  </p>

  <h2>Sharing your data</h2>
  <p>
    We do not sell your personal data. We share it only with service providers who process it on
    our behalf under contract — for example our email-delivery provider (Resend) and our website
    analytics provider (Google Analytics) — and only to the extent needed to provide their
    service. We may also disclose data where required by law or competent authority.
  </p>

  <h2>International transfers</h2>
  <p>
    Some of our service providers process data outside the UAE. Where personal data is transferred
    across borders, we take steps to ensure an adequate level of protection consistent with the
    PDPL.
  </p>

  <h2>Retention</h2>
  <p>
    We keep personal data only for as long as necessary for the purposes set out above, or as
    required to meet legal, accounting, or regulatory obligations, after which it is deleted or
    anonymised.
  </p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>Subject to the PDPL, you have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>access the personal data we hold about you;</li>
    <li>have inaccurate or incomplete data corrected;</li>
    <li>request deletion of your data;</li>
    <li>restrict or object to certain processing;</li>
    <li>withdraw consent at any time, where processing is based on consent;</li>
    <li>request that your data be transferred to you or another controller; and</li>
    <li>lodge a complaint with the UAE Data Office.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us using the details below.</p>

  <h2>Security</h2>
  <p>
    We apply appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect personal data against
    unauthorised access, loss, or misuse. No method of transmission or storage is completely
    secure, but we work to safeguard your information at every stage.
  </p>

  <h2>Children</h2>
  <p>This website and our services are intended for business audiences and are not directed at individuals under 18.</p>

  <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The date at the top of this page shows when it was last revised; material changes will be made prominent where appropriate.</p>

  <h2>Contact us</h2>
  <p>
    Emerge Digital IT Solutions LLC, Dubai, United Arab Emirates.<br />
    Email: <a href="mailto:rami@emergedigital.com">rami@emergedigital.com</a>
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
